</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l3">Gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Jnchenhof<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l5">vmb erbſchaft die er <add><ab facs="#facs_125_r2l4">vnd ſein weib </ab></add>
<expan>cʒehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mainen auf des Tecʒels hof bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l6">vnd auch gen <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Ebner
                        von eins hofs <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü Pöllingen /
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l7">wir <expan>ew<ex>re</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> /
                        vnd <expan>diſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l8">cʒü rede geſacʒt / . vnd die
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns geantwurt / daʒ ſie das
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l13"><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~
                                <expan>Jnchenhof<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_line_1576570278863_2194">vnd
                                    <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> weib </ab></add> fremde nem / .
                        daʒ er ſölıch ſache von Jn awſgeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l15"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürbring / . wan ſie nichts wiſſen / daʒ ſie
                        mit Jm <add><ab facs="#facs_125_r2l12">noch <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                                weıb </ab></add>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> er noch ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l14">weıb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l17">mit Jn cʒeſchicken haben /
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> Jm <add><ab facs="#facs_125_r2l16">noch ir
                            </ab></add> ſchuldig ſein / . Doch dewht
                            <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l19"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Jnchenhof<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_r2l18">vnd ſeın weıb </ab></add> / daʒ ſie
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu
                            <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıht
                            <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l20"><expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> darvmb
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir Jn <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_line_1576570312646_2216"><expan>ıre<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab></add>
<expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_line_1576570315688_2221"><expan>ıre<ex>m</ex></expan>
</ab></add>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l21">gewalt <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> wenn wir des <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_125_r2l23">werden ſo <del rend="strikethrough">ſie </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_125_line_1576570319370_2226">dıſelben
                                        <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan>
</ab></add> anheim ſind / vnd wo etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_125" id="62r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Jnchenhof<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> umb erbschaft, die er <add>und sein weib</add>
<expan>cze hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mainen auf des Teczels hof bey uns, und
                        auch gen <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Ebner von eins hofs
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czü Pöllingen,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>re</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
                        und <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> darumb czü rede gesaczt; und die
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns geantwurt, daz sie das
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Jnchenhof<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>und <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> weib</add> fremde nem, daz er sölich
                        sache von in awsgeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürbring, wan sie nichts wissen, daz sie mit
                        im <add>noch <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> weib</add>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> er noch sein weib mit in cze schicken haben
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> im <add>noch ir</add> schuldig sein.
                        Doch dewht <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Jnchenhof<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>und sein weib</add>, daz sie <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht
                            <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan>, darumb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                            <add><expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan></add>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, wenn wir des <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
                        werden, so <add>diselben <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add> anheim sind. Und wo etc.</ab>
</div>
